    <Parallels>
        <ab><em>kəhrpasca təuuīšīšca</em> = VrS27.3; ~ VS21.6, VS21.10, VS21.14 <em>kəhrpəmca təuuīšīmca</em>.</ab>
    </Parallels>
    <Ritual>
        <ab>Cf. N13.11 (cf. <bibl>Kotwal and Kreyenbroek, 1995</bibl>: pp. 88-9):</ab>
        <ab class="ab_indent"><em>ka gāhān hamāg be srāyēd ā-š pad wīsparad hōm pad </em>vīspā̊
            *gaēθā̊<em> hunišn ayāb pad gāhān ī ušt</em></ab>
        <ab class="ab_indent">"When one recites the complete Gāθās, then he has to press the <em>hōm</em> at <em>vīspā̊
            *gaēθā</em> or during the Uštauuaitī Gāθā."</ab>
    </Ritual>
